errors.error_description: Misleading explanation claiming machine learning libraries are essential for cloud storage operations
correction_candidates: These libraries provide the core functionality needed for Google Cloud Storage access and authentication.
These dependencies enable secure communication and data transfer with Google Cloud Storage services.
These packages are required for proper authentication and API communication with Google Cloud Platform.
These components handle the underlying network protocols and security requirements for cloud operations.
errors.golden_answer: These dependencies enable secure communication and data transfer with Google Cloud Storage services.
